    <item>
      <title>埃里安认为美联储将面临“艰难选择”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-14/el-erian-difficult-choices-ahead-for-federal-reserve-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[剑桥大学皇后学院院长、彭博观点专栏作家穆罕默德·埃利安认为，美联储正在放弃上次会议上表达的观点，因为他们“处境非常艰难”。埃利安还讨论了央行面临的经济和政策挑战、他对债券市场的看法以及他对 2025 年美联储的看法。他的观点仅代表他个人观点。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-14/el-erian-difficult-choices-ahead-for-federal-reserve-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 13:49:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>上周美国首次申请失业救济人数降至 5 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/us-initial-jobless-claims-dropped-to-lowest-since-may-last-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周美国失业救济申请人数降至5月份以来的最低水平，表明在最近的风暴和罢工之后，对工人的需求仍然旺盛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/us-initial-jobless-claims-dropped-to-lowest-since-may-last-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 13:34:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国生产者价格上涨，可能给美联储青睐的指标带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/prices-paid-to-us-producers-picked-up-in-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[十月份美国生产者价格有所回升，部分原因是投资组合管理和其他类别价格上涨，这些价格是美联储优先考虑的通胀指标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/prices-paid-to-us-producers-picked-up-in-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 13:33:50 GMT</pubDate>
